Package gov.nasa.jpl.aerie.json

Class BasicParsers

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.jpl.aerie.json.BasicParsers
public abstract class BasicParsers extends Object
A namespace for primitive parsers and essential combinators. Non-primitive mappers and niche combinators should be given their own top-level classes.
